        "text": "=I need you to interpret the input fast and only give me back which of the following array objects fits most: \n- short_answer, for easy questions \n- long_answer, when extra retrieval or research is required\n- tool_use, when the request can't be fullfilled with only a text response\n- job, when it looks like the request will need more then a single agent call\n\nYou must pick only  1, and always 1\n\nYour response format should be precisly like this example:\n{\"RequestType\": \"tool_use\"}\n\nMy input: '{{$json.input}}'.",
