    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "1. Tasks (The Atoms)\nThese are \"one-and-done\" interactions. You provide an input, and you expect a single, immediate output.\n\nScope: Minutes of work.\n\nRelationship: Usually maps to one atomic intent (e.g., just Synthesis or just Generation).\n\nExample: \"Summarize this PDF\" or \"Write a Python script to rename files.\"",
        "height": 224,
        "width": 432
      },
      "id": "444b572f-748a-4c88-8d74-7604a2a8a5fc",
      "name": "Sticky Note10",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -1872,
        240
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "2 Projects (The Molecules)\nA project requires the AI to maintain context over several steps or provide a multi-part deliverable. It’s \"elaborate\" because the output isn't a single thing, but a collection.\n\nScope: Hours or days of iterative work.\n\nRelationship: Chains multiple atomic intents together (e.g., Query the market, then Generate a report, then Transform it into a slide deck).\n\nExample: \"Design a 4-week workout plan based on my health data and create a shopping list for week one.\"",
        "height": 256,
        "width": 512
      },
      "id": "26007a90-d711-4fab-be19-35201bafbdaa",
      "name": "Sticky Note14",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -1424,
        240
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "3 Missions (The Jobs)\nThis is what you described with the \"online business\" example. You aren't asking for a file; you’re asking for an outcome. This requires the AI to act as an agent—making decisions, self-correcting, and interacting with the world.\n\nScope: Weeks or months; often ongoing.\n\nRelationship: An orchestration of all atomic intents plus Agency (action).\n\nExample: \"Find a gap in the pet tech market, launch a Shopify store, and manage the social media presence to hit $1k in sales.\"",
        "height": 256,
        "width": 512
      },
      "id": "798db962-8abf-447a-b9b1-c3b6a48807c5",
      "name": "Sticky Note17",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -896,
        240
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
